snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - XB1/PS4/PC/SWITCH - Goku Character Intro
snippet.description:
Here comes the very first gameplay of the base Goku: a new character to be added to the roster of DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ early August.
Watch him unleash the Kaioken formidable power and the iconic Super Spirit Bomb!
